message: “Our main focus areas are educating youth and the communities about the issues of human trafficking ...” - Bill Woolf, Founder of the Just Ask Prevention Project.

data.description: (From left): Kavita Nanavati, Mrs. District of Columbia USA Ambassador 2018 who emceed the event; Nancy Rivard, President of Airline Ambassadors; Bill Woolf, Founder of Just Ask; and Jodi O’Hern, Director of Just Ask. Photo by Steve Hibbard.
data.title: A Night to Help End Human Trafficking
